//Helios-Lidar UI translations. Keyed by ISO 639-1 language code.
//
//Strings hold the user-visible text only; the glossary definitions
//under the help block stay English-only for now because the level
//of GIS jargon there would need a real translator pass to be useful
//in seven other languages. The keys we DO translate cover every
//string a casual visitor reads from the top of the page down to
//the result section.
//
//A value can contain inline HTML (links, em). innerHTML is used for
//those, which is safe because the values are static and shipped in
//this module, not user-controlled.
//
//Translation pass done by the project author for the language pairs
//he speaks fluently (FR), and best-effort for the others using
//standard mapping conventions for technical terms; PRs welcome.

